OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780419953
OL,3,CHow new bridge in Nottingham will
OL,4,Cbenefit Forest and County football fans
OL,6,FNottingham's new Waterside Bridge has
OL,7,Fofficially opened today, bringing huge
OL,8,Fbenefits for walkers, cyclists and
OL,9,Fboth Notts County and Nottingham
OL,10,FForest fans.
OL,12,FThe structure stretches over the River
OL,13,FTrent between Trent Basin and Lady
OL,14,FBay. As part of the development, the
OL,15,Fnewly-widened and surfaced riverside
OL,16,Ffootpath on the south side of the
OL,17,Friver has also reopened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
