PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780419953
OL,3,CHow new bridge in Nottingham will
OL,4,Cbenefit Forest and County football fans
OL,6,FIt's the first crossing to be built
OL,7,Fover the river in the city in more
OL,8,Fthan 65 years. It aims to provide a
OL,9,Fsafe, traffic-free, shorter route for
OL,10,Fpedestrians, cyclists and runners
OL,11,Fbetween the developing Trent Basin
OL,12,Farea of Sneinton, Lady Bay and West
OL,13,FBridgford.
OL,15,FIt will also be vital during football
OL,16,Fand other sports matches, giving fans
OL,17,Fa safe way to cross the river to get
OL,18,Fto Nottingham Rugby Club, Nottingham
OL,19,FForest's City Ground and Notts
OL,20,FCounty's Meadow Lane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780419953
OL,3,CHow new bridge in Nottingham will
OL,4,Cbenefit Forest and County football fans
OL,6,FWhat benefits will the new bridge
OL,7,Fprovide?
OL,9,FThe bridge will connect Sneinton and
OL,10,FLady Bay, and open up access to green
OL,11,Fspaces on either side of the river
OL,12,Fincluding Colwick Country Park and
OL,13,FHolme Pierrepont and Skylarks nature
OL,14,Freserve.
OL,16,FAs a result, new walking and cycling
OL,17,Froutes will be created.
OL,19,FTraffic pressures on both Trent Bridge
OL,20,Fand Lady Bay bridge will be alleviated
OL,21,Fthrough increased sustainable travel.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
