OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780419953
OL,3,CHow new bridge in Nottingham will
OL,4,Cbenefit Forest and County football fans
OL,6,FHow big is the bridge?
OL,8,FWaterside Bridge is 87 metres long and
OL,9,Fweighs 175 tonnes.
OL,11,FWhat will be done to celebrate the
OL,12,Fopening?
OL,14,FChildren from schools in the city
OL,15,Fattended a ribbon cutting ceremony,
OL,16,Falong with councillors and other
OL,17,Fofficials to declare the crossing open.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
