PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1780419953
OL,3,CHow new bridge in Nottingham will
OL,4,Cbenefit Forest and County football fans
OL,6,FThere will also be a free community
OL,7,Ffun day on Sunday, June 14, with
OL,8,Factivities and stalls on both the
OL,9,Fnorth and south banks of the river.
OL,11,FThese will include food and drink,
OL,12,Fcommunity performances, free
OL,13,Factivities for children and adults
OL,14,Fincluding crafts, face painting,
OL,15,Fgames, a focus on STEM (science
OL,16,Ftechnology, engineering and maths) and
OL,17,Fsports activities.
OL,19,FTIMELINE OF BRIDGE BUILDING
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
